high_descs: Go straight ahead and when you reach the saddle, turn left. Turn right. At the end of the cabinet, cross to the right. Go straight ahead, turn right.
Take the tomato on the left.
Turn right. Go ahead, before the end of the cabinet, turn around.
Place the tomato over the sink.
Turn around, when you reach the wall, turn right. Approach the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, take the tomato, close the refrigerator.
Turn around. Turn left. Approach the sink.
Place the tomato over the sink, behind the one over there.
anns.task_desc: Find two tomatoes and place them over the sink.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the countertop on your right
Pick up tomato from the counter top
Turn back and take few steps and turn left and take immediate left turn to reach the back side of the sink
Place tomato on the sink
Turn right, walk past the pot, through the living room, and through the bedroom door on the left up to the foot of the fridge
Pick up tomato on the fridge
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the sink
Place tomato on the sink
anns.task_desc: Collecting tomato from different places and arranging them on a sink

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the counter top.
Pick up tomato from the counter top.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the sink.
Place tomato on the sink.
Head straight towards the fridge by turning around and turning left.
Pick up tomato from the counter top.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the sink.
Place tomato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collecting tomato from different places and arranging them on a sink.
